views of customers with notes and recommendations regarding creditworthiness Credit Analyst requirements This section should list the essential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Credit Analyst requirements Bachelor\u2019s degree in business, finance or related field Must have strong computer skills Excellent analytical skills and high attention to detail Must be an excellent communicator Previous experience in a financial setting is an asset Ability to make customers feel valued and provide excellent customer experience Credit Analyst related job titles: Credit Administration Analyst Senior Credit Analyst Auto Finance Credit Underwriter Commercial Credit Analyst Fixed Income Structured Credit Analyst Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
